      "date": "2012-07-19 17:28:09.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 6: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64, CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/870f4b74-d1c2-11e1-8fae-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
