        "subject": "LU-1575 ptlrpc: fix for the flock policy combinations",
        "message": "LU-1575 ptlrpc: fix for the flock policy combinations\n\nThe current patch is intended to fix the issue with incorrect flock\npolicy determining. This issue is observed when 1.8 clients\nwith updated flock policies try to connect to the 2.x servers.\nThis patch intended for 2.x servers to let recognition for\nupdated 1.8 clients.\n\nXyratex-bug-id: MRP-489\nReviewed-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nReviewed-by: Andriy Skulysh <andriy_skulysh@xyratex.com>\nSigned-off-by: Iurii Golovach <iurii_golovach@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: I4a834080a9a8389912636e628dfcbd0dfc103f64\n"
